import React, { PureComponent, Fragment } from 'react' import Header2 from '../public/header2' import Footer from '../public/footer' import { Redirect } from 'react-router-dom' import Studentheaderlayout from '../public/studentheaderlayout' import api from '../public/api' import Moment from 'moment' class Studentdashboard extends PureComponent { constructor(props) { super(props) this.state = { redirect:true, loading:false } } componentWillMount(){ const auth= localStorage.getItem('userprofile') let studentprofile=[]; let userprofile =[]; let counter=0 if(auth == undefined || auth ==null){ this.setState({redirect:true}) } else{ var now = Moment(new Date()); //todays date api.post("/auth/me",{token:JSON.parse(auth).token}).then(res=>{ // console.log("userprofile",res.data.user) if(res.data.success==true){ this.setState({userprofile:res.data.user}) userprofile=res.data.user api.get(`/student/getdata/${parseInt(userprofile.id)}`).then(res=>{ console.log("studentdata ",res.data) if(res.data.success==true){ this.setState({studentprofile:res.data.data.rows}) let totaliq=0; let alliq=0; studentprofile.map(elem=>{ alliq+= Number(elem.income.substring(1)) var end = Moment( elem.updatedAt.substring(0,10)); // another date var duration = Moment.duration(now.diff(end)); var days = duration.asDays(); if(parseInt(days) <=7){ totalbalances += Number(elem.iq) // this.setState({totalmonthbalance:totalbalances}); } return counter }) } }) } }) } } componentDidMount(){ this.setState({loading:true}) } render() { const {redirect,loading} = this.state; if(redirect ==false){ return } return (loading ==false)?
